Package: IRTscoring
Title: Flexible Item Response Theory Scoring
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Marcus", "Waldman", email = "marcus.waldman@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides flexible estimation methods for unidimensional and
    multidimensional Item Response Theory (IRT) models. Supports MAP,
    Variational Bayes (including Pathfinder), Laplace Approximation, and
    full Bayesian MCMC estimation via Stan, as well as alternative optimizers
    via BridgeStan.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
